      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it garage-parked and sparkling clean. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
