    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-level condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS high-pressure actuation. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a 3.62:1 M-Variable differential. Mechanically flawless, the rod bearing service and subframe reinforcement have been proactively addressed using reinforced plating. The chassis remains taut, riding on original-spec Sachs dampers with zero fluid seepage. The exterior retains its factory-applied Alpine White finish with deep luster, while the Nappa leather interior shows negligible bolster compression. A true driver\u2019s machine with surgical throttle response and a linear torque curve, maintained to a standard that satisfies the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service records. Pristine interior and exterior. Mechanically perfect.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
