    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom-ready condition, this vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream. The original paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, preserved under a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the dashboard is free of UV damage, and the original floor mats are spotless. Every button and switch operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this car has been pampered, stored in a climate-controlled garage and followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all records documented. It drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line\u2014tight suspension, responsive steering, and a flawless powertrain. Included are both original keys, the owner\u2019s manual, and a clean title. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved example that looks, smells, and performs like a new vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
